{
    "key": 22894,
    "messages": [
        {
            "id": "VeilstoneGym_Text_MayleneIntro",
            "en_US": [
                "Hello.\n",
                "I\u2019m pleased to meet you.\r",
                "I\u2019m Maylene, and I\u2019m the Gym\n",
                "Leader.\r",
                "I don\u2019t really know what it means to\n",
                "be strong, or how I got to be the\f",
                "Gym Leader.\r",
                "But I will do the best I can as the\n",
                "Gym Leader.\r",
                "I take battling very seriously.\n",
                "Whenever you\u2019re ready!\r"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "VeilstoneGym_Text_BeatMaylene",
            "en_US": [
                "...OK.\n",
                "You win.\r",
                "That was a tough loss.\n",
                "I learned a lot from it.\r",
                "Please, accept this Gym Badge.\r"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "VeilstoneGym_Text_MayleneReceiveBadge",
            "en_US": [
                "{STRVAR_1 3, 0, 0} received\n",
                "the Cobble Badge from Maylene."
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "VeilstoneGym_Text_MayleneExplainBadge",
            "en_US": [
                "Um... I should explain about that\n",
                "official Pok\u00e9mon League Gym Badge.\r",
                "With it, you can use the hidden move Fly\n",
                "outside of battle.\r",
                "Oh, and since you now have four Gym\n",
                "Badges, Pok\u00e9mon obtained in trades\f",
                "will obey you up to Lv. 50.\r",
                "Oh, and please take this as well.\r"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "VeilstoneGym_Text_MayleneExplainTM60",
            "en_US": [
                "That {STRVAR_1 8, 0, 0} contains the move\n",
                "{STRVAR_1 6, 1, 0}.\r",
                "Um... That move inflicts damage,\n",
                "and it robs the target\u2019s HP."
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "VeilstoneGym_Text_MayleneAfterBadge",
            "en_US": [
                "Gee, I\u2019m hungry...\r",
                "Oh, sorry, it\u2019s nothing.\n",
                "I didn\u2019t say anything.\r",
                "{STRVAR_1 3, 0, 0}, I can\u2019t explain what\n",
                "it means to be strong.\r",
                "I don\u2019t know how much effort goes\n",
                "into being strong...\r",
                "But being with Pok\u00e9mon lets us\n",
                "keep making the effort, doesn\u2019t it?"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "VeilstoneGym_Text_GymGuideBeforeBadge",
            "en_US": [
                "Hey, there!\n",
                "How\u2019s it going, Champ-to-be?\r",
                "The Gym Leader is a user of\n",
                "Fighting-type Pok\u00e9mon.\r",
                "She\u2019d be a terror against Normal-type\n",
                "Pok\u00e9mon.\r",
                "But! And it\u2019s a big but!\n",
                "Just between you and me...\r",
                "Maylene, the Gym Leader, said Flying-\n",
                "and Psychic-type Pok\u00e9mon could be\f",
                "real trouble for her!\r",
                "If you want to battle her, smack the\n",
                "punching bags along the rails.\r",
                "You have to hit those bags hard!"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "VeilstoneGym_Text_GymGuideAfterBadge",
            "en_US": [
                "Oh! {STRVAR_1 3, 0, 0}!\n",
                "You\u2019ve beaten the Gym Leader!\r",
                "Of course, I thought you\u2019d win."
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "VeilstoneGym_Text_GymStatueBeforeBadge",
            "en_US": [
                "Veilstone City Pok\u00e9mon Gym\n",
                "Leader: Maylene\r",
                "Certified Trainers:\n",
                "{STRVAR_1 3, 1, 0}"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "VeilstoneGym_Text_GymStatueAfterBadge",
            "en_US": [
                "Veilstone City Pok\u00e9mon Gym\n",
                "Leader: Maylene\r",
                "Certified Trainers:\n",
                "{STRVAR_1 3, 0, 0}\f",
                "{STRVAR_1 3, 1, 0}"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "VeilstoneGym_Text_GoodDeedEveryDay",
            "en_US": "A good deed for every day."
        },
        {
            "id": "VeilstoneGym_Text_TreasureEveryEncounter",
            "en_US": [
                "Treasure every encounter,\n",
                "for it is unique."
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "VeilstoneGym_Text_OneDayAtATime",
            "en_US": "One day at a time."
        },
        {
            "id": "GymExit_Text_MustDefeatLeader_VeilstoneGym",
            "en_US": [
                "You can\u2019t leave until you\n",
                "defeat the Gym Leader!\r"
            ]
        }
    ]
}